1. *Plaća* se udvostručila. (The salary was doubled.)
2. *Plaćaju* mi se dva puta mesečno. (I get paid twice a month.)
3. *Plaćen* je visok bonus. (A high bonus was paid.)
4. *Plaćala* sam svoj račun. (I paid my bill.)
5. *Plaćen* je preko bankovnog računa. (It was paid via bank account.)
6. *Plaćaju* mi za dodatne usluge. (They are paying me for additional services.)